			<p><span class="smallcaps"><strong>Sparrow</strong></span> lives in New York City. He does a lot of his writing on the subway, though &ldquo;if you write on the subway, people think you&rsquo;re crazy &mdash; especially if you look like me. There&rsquo;s a type of Bag Person who writes an endless list of numbers, or a diary, on long rolls of paper, in very tiny print. I am mistaken for this person.&rdquo;</p><a href="/contributors/sparrow" class="block-contributor-link link-alt small">More From This Contributor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>		</div>
	</div>
</div>

							</footer>
						</article>


